933]] \n| {{Composition bar|2692|11424|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 77\n|- \n! [[1937 Danish regional elections|1937]] \n| {{Composition bar|2374|11425|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 318\n|- \n! [[1943 Danish regional elections|1943]] \n| {{Composition bar|2217|10569|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 157\n|- \n! [[1946 Danish regional elections|1946]] \n| {{Composition bar|2519|11488|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 302\n|- \n! [[1950 Danish regional elections|1950]] \n| {{Composition bar|2342|11499|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 177\n|- \n! [[1954 Danish regional elections|1954]] \n| {{Composition bar|2353|11505|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 11\n|- \n! [[1958 Danish regional elections|1958]] \n| {{Composition bar|2405|11529|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 52\n|- \n! [[1962 Danish regional elections|1962]] \n| {{Composition bar|2196|11414|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 209\n|- \n! [[1966 Danish regional elections|1966]] \n| {{Composition bar|1747|10005|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 449\n|- \n! [[1970 Danish regional elections|1970]] \n| {{Composition bar|1080|4677|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 667\n|- \n! [[1974 Danish regional elections|1974]] \n| {{Composition bar|1277|4735|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 197\n|- \n! [[1978 Danish regional elections|1978]] \n| {{Composition bar|1155|4759|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 122\n|- \n! [[1981 Danish regional elections|1981]] \n| {{Composition bar|1240|4769|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 85\n|- \n! [[1985 Danish regional elections|1985]] \n| {{Composition bar|1201|4773|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 39\n|- \n! [[1989 Danish regional elections|1989]] \n| {{Composition bar|1261|4737|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 60\n|- \n! [[1993 Danish regional elections|1993]] \n| {{Composition bar|1601|4703|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 340\n|- \n! [[1997 Danish regional elections|1997]] \n| {{Composition bar|1557|4685|#25587E}}\n| {{decrease}} 44\n|- \n! [[2001 Danish local elections|2001]] \n| {{Composition bar|1666|4647|#25587E}}\n| {{increase}} 109\n|-\n! [[2005 Danish local elections|2005]]\n|{{Composition bar